[VS2-332] Collection data modalities

Background:
TBC

User Story:
As a Data Consumer Lead, I want to specify data modalities for each study so that data sourcing and access are clearly defined.

Acceptance criteria:
GIVEN an Open Access Collection WHEN recording data modalities for it THEN selection of particular data modality is included or excluded for each study is enabled.
GIVEN an Open Access Collection WHEN recording data modalities for it THEN selection plural data modalities for a single Study is enabled.
GIVEN an Open Access Collection WHEN recording data modalities for it THEN no Study has blank data modality record.